ğŸ—‚ï¸ Detected Classes

The model detects and classifies the following 11 categories:
	1.	Graffiti
	2.	Faded Signage
	3.	Potholes
	4.	Garbage
	5.	Construction on Road
	6.	Broken Signage
	7.	Bad Streetlight
	8.	Bad Billboard
	9.	Sand on Road
	10.	Cluttered Sidewalk
	11.	Unkept Facade

